Have fun!

This is one of the, soon to be, many Castle Defender maps created be myself and others. This one of those "New Trend" deals so, pass it around. The objective of the map is for the terrorists to get inside of the counter-terrorist 'Castle' and kill all of them. The terrorists do so be traveling around the castle on either the walkway or on the T-Train which travels in a square around the castle at 350 pixels a second.  There is one large platform, whith breakable walls around it and a tall sniper tower, for the ct and two smaller platforms for the terrorists. On one of the terrorist's platforms, is a small walkway that extends out when the two 'main' doors gaurding the ct's castle are destroyed. The platforms are floating and if you fall off any of the platforms, you switch teams and wait for the round to end. This map would be excellent for those with the death match mod for CSS. This map, like many of my others, is GREAT for any size lan party, but it is also enjoyable on an online server with many players. Have fun and please let me know what you think. Oh and if you like the idea, please spread the Castle Defenders trend around.

This is a single-player (though more than 1 player can be on the map at the same time) CSS obstacle course training map.  You must make your way through the 4 areas: Earth, Air, Fire, Water in the fastest time possible.  You are timed and the results are displayed on the digital display in the starting area.  Entry into each area will be noted on the status board.
You are timed from when you jump into the Earth zone to when you touch the exit door.  There are 6 T and 6 CT spawns but everyone should be on the same team so you can watch progress on the radar.
Created for use in the [NtN] Clan Olympics, have fun and no speed hacks!

Place the Norbit_v1.BSP file under your folder: program files->steam->steamApps->*username->maps


* username must be shifted with your own username

This map is based on the game musical chairs. instead, i made it work with rooms. Everyone starts with a knife in a pretty small area. while you are knifing you will hear some music and when it stops some doors will open. only 1 player is able to get in a room (and with luck 2 people can - but if they do that in the last round both will still die).

Unlike with the previous versions there is now only a version with knifes.

Each round is seperated in 5 shorter rounds. The doors that open in each round are random
round 1 opens 20 doors
round 2 opens 14 doors
round 3 opens 8 doors
round 4 opens 4 doors
round 5 opens 1 door
On average this should take: 2 minutes

Changes since b2:
- Sub rounds are now made shorter (10-20 seconds)
- More weird music and boring ones removed
- People now get autohealed back to 100hp so only a backstab will kill now
- Changed the look of the map
- Added details like the background
- Doors are now transparent so you can see the people die in front of you (coused a problem in seeing which doors are open - will be changed in the next version!)

This map is based on the game musical chairs. instead, i made it work with rooms. Everyone starts with a knife in a pretty small area. while you are knifing you will hear some music and when it stops some doors will open (the first round all will open as there are only 20 and when there are more in the map many will die anyway). only 1 player should be able to get in a room (and with luck 2 people can - but if they do that in the last round both will still die). There are 2 versions of this map! - A version with knifes - A version without knifes Both versions are in this package and are only diffirent in having the knife or not. Each round is seperated in 5 shorter rounds. The doors that open in each round are random round 1 opens 20 doors round 2 opens 14 doors round 3 opens 8 doors round 4 opens 4 doors round 5 opens 1 door On average this should take: 2 minutes and 15 seconds The knife version is recommended for large server so not too many die in the first round. Note: if people have downloading sounds disabled then they wont hear the music but they hear the doors open.

This map is based on the game musical chairs. instead, i made it work with rooms. Everyone starts with a knife in a pretty small area. while you are knifing you will hear some music and when it stops some doors will open (the first round all will open as there are only 20 and when there are more in the map many will die anyway). only 1 player should be able to get in a room (thats why i have b1a as in b1 this was bugged so still more were able to get in). There are 2 versions of this map! Both in this package A version with knifes This version has only 5 rounds and everyone spawns with a knife. this version is best for large servers as the no knife version lets too many people die in the first round. round 1 opens 20 doors round 2 opens 14 doors round 3 opens 8 doors round 4 opens 4 doors round 5 opens 1 door The doors that open are random Average round is about 130 seconds A version without knifes This version has 10 rounds where the rounds are this way: round 1 - 20 doors round 2 - 16 doors round 3 - 13 doors round 4 - 10 doors round 5 - 8 doors round 6 - 6 doors round 7 - 4 doors round 8 - 3 doors round 9 - 2 doors round 10 - 1 door This version is best played with about 24 players. as there will be many deaths in the first round with more players and no deaths when less then 20 and with only 10 players there are 3 rounds without deaths. Also, the later rounds are shorter to prevent people waiting too long. Average round is about 200 seconds Note: people that have downloading sounds to off can still hear the doors open so they shouldnt get a problem.

This is, almost, the exact replica of the original Pacman level one. Every 15 seconds, one terrorist, in the middle box, is let out of the cage, as a ghost with a knife, to attack the counter-terrorists who are defenseless. The goal of the Ts is to kill all of the CTs. The goal of the CTs is to destroy all of the "yellow squares" put strategically around the map, by pressing up against them. When all 168 "yellow squares" are destroyed, all  players CT and T are killed, the round ends and CTs get 10 points. Enjoy.
